{"tid":2061442,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★網傳「五毛」降價變「兩毛」？經濟差連網軍收入都受影響","createTime":"2020-06-12T11:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T12:19:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4cf54d8c56392b6b976c4e15220e66263a43fcc7","tid":2061442,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T11:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2665000/2668700/wang00_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2665000%2F2668700%2Fwang00_1024.jpg&h=4e78da3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n内地網軍被稱爲「五毛」，原因是有傳每出一次帖都能賺取 5 毛人民幣的酬勞。在今年 4 月，有媒體報道指「五毛」成功加薪，成功爭取每帖「七毛」甚至「八毛」酬勞，加薪幅度足足有 14.3％。可惜的是，近日網傳「五毛」因經濟環境差而被壓價，也許大家日後要改口稱呼他們為「兩毛」了。<br />\n<br />\n-近日網傳網軍「五毛」因經濟環境差而降價，變成「兩毛」<br />\n-網傳内地社群網站以「兩毛」聘請「寫評論兼職」，長評論連圖亦只有 4 毛<br />\n-在今年 4 月，有報道曾指「五毛」加薪至「七毛」甚至「八毛」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2668700/%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E3%80%8C%E4%BA%94%E6%AF%9B%E3%80%8D%E9%99%8D%E5%83%B9%E8%AE%8A%E3%80%8C%E5%85%A9%E6%AF%9B%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%9F%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%B7%AE%E9%80%A3%E7%B6%B2%E8%BB%8D%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E9%83%BD%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2668700%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%25AF%259B%25E3%2580%258D%25E9%2599%258D%25E5%2583%25B9%25E8%25AE%258A%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25AF%259B%25E3%2580%258D%25EF%25BC%259F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjBZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=b7025176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2668700/%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E3%80%8C%E4%BA%94%E6%AF%9B%E3%80%8D%E9%99%8D%E5%83%B9%E8%AE%8A%E3%80%8C%